<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{leave_title}}</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');

    * {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif !important;
    }

    body {

      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      /* max-width: 600px; 
      background-color: #fff;
      */
      padding: 20px auto;

      border: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info,
    .employee-info {
      /* padding: 10px; */
      border-radius: 4px;
      /* background-color: #f9f9f9; */
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .info h2,
    .employee-info h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .info p,
    .employee-info p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center !important;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #44c4f2 !important;
    }

    .v1footer {
      text-align: center !important;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #44c4f2 !important;
    }

    .footer p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #000;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Banner Image -->
    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dprcylred/image/upload/v1742070266/bdpbih5xiopoe7ho2g6g.png"
      alt="Company Banner" style="width: 100%;" />

    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <strong>{{admin}},</strong></p>

      <p>We hope you're doing well. You have received a **leave request** from an employee that requires your
        attention. Below are the details of the request:</p>

      <div class="employee-info">
        <h2>Employee Information</h2>
        <p style="text-transform: capitalize;"><strong>Name:</strong> {{employee_name}}</p>
        <p><strong>Employee ID:</strong> {{employee_id}}</p>
        <p><strong>Department:</strong> {{employee_department}}</p>
        <p><strong>Designation:</strong> {{employee_designation}}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="info">
        <h2>Leave Request Details</h2>
        <p><strong>Request Date:</strong> {{request_date}}</p>
        <p><strong>Leave Type:</strong> {{leave_type}}</p>
        <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{from_date}} to {{to_date}} ({{no_of_days}} days)</p>
        <p><strong>Reason for Leave:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
      </div>




      <p>If you require further details regarding this leave request, feel free to contact the **HR department**.
      </p>

      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p><strong>HR Team</strong><br>Quantum Works Private Limited</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; Quantum Works Private Limited. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>For HR-related queries, contact<br /> <a
          href="mailto:mailto:hr@quantumworks.in">mailto:hr@quantumworks.in</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>